                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.512/717.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Special Agent <persName type="to">Silliman</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-07-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 23, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department has following telegram from Consul General, Monterey, relating to
                    mining decree of March 1:</p>
                <p>[Quotes Mr. Hanna’s July 22.]</p>
                <p>Urgently endeavor obtain desired modification and ask that notice thereof be
                    given by telegraph.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adee.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
